
* Add optional configure features.  Examples

	--[en/dis]able-debug
	--[en/dis]able-release
	--[en/dis]able-warnings
	--[en/dis]able-threads

* Add platform-checking code.  Examples:

	Poshlib - http://www.writeportablecode.com/
	Boost Config - http://www.boost.org/libs/config/

* Create a branch for distributions written exclusively in C++.

	- Add Autotool macros for C++.
	http://autoconf-archive.cryp.to/macros-by-category.html#CXX

